body:
Hey guys! Here I am with a new forum game, that I thought of while doing some quotes for an English assignment. I have no idea how this'll go, but I just thought I'd give it a try.

How it works: Basically, you say a relatively well-known quote from a movie, and the next person has to guess the movie, and say another quote, for the next person to guess.

I'll start, with a fairly easy quote:
"May the odds be ever in your favor"
